cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.ST, cs.SI. 

The paper describes a probabilistic programming platform for querying data, which involves techniques from database systems (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), statistics (cs.ST), and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper's focus on probabilistic modeling and Bayesian inference also suggests a strong connection to cs.ST.
